videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Cincinnati's Addaya Moore tries to score in the paint, but Olivia Nelson-Ododa blocks the shot away.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn's Nelson-Ododa swats shot out of bounds) 2020/02/26

videos.headline: UConn's Nelson-Ododa swats shot out of bounds

videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield passes over the entire Cincinnati defense to find Anna Makurat, who finishes through contact for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Dangerfield dishes dime to Makurat for and-1 bucket) 2020/02/26

videos.headline: Dangerfield dishes dime to Makurat for and-1 bucket
